00:04:23.650 --> 00:04:25.030
LATHA PALANIAPPAN:
Insulin and blood sugar.

00:04:25.030 --> 00:04:25.720
Great answer.

00:04:25.720 --> 00:04:27.580
So that's the absolute
correct answer.

00:04:27.580 --> 00:04:29.410
So we try to check
your blood sugar.

00:04:29.410 --> 00:04:33.730
So we check either
a fasting number

00:04:33.730 --> 00:04:36.430
in the morning of
your blood sugar,

00:04:36.430 --> 00:04:40.540
