00:04:44.830 --> 00:04:46.715
And we can measure those levels.

00:04:46.715 --> 00:04:48.340
And then, another
way that we can do it

00:04:48.340 --> 00:04:51.850
is through an oral
glucose tolerance test.

00:04:51.850 --> 00:04:56.780
And that's sort of
drinking a glucose load,

00:04:56.780 --> 00:04:58.930
and then checking your
glucose after two hours

00:04:58.930 --> 00:05:01.480
to see how your body
processes glucose.

00:05:01.480 --> 00:05:03.940
