00:39:14.340 --> 00:39:16.750
they're able to integrate
some of that information

00:39:16.750 --> 00:39:18.220
into city planning.

00:39:18.220 --> 00:39:21.520
India is at a stage where now
you're saying, OK, there--

00:39:21.520 --> 00:39:26.080
to prevent this migration from
rural areas to urban areas,

00:39:26.080 --> 00:39:29.530
and all the consequences
