There are probably 400
to 500 cities in India

00:39:35.500 --> 00:39:38.170
that are saying, we need
to create infrastructure

00:39:38.170 --> 00:39:40.670
so people stay where they are.

00:39:40.670 --> 00:39:42.910
So understanding,
how does that work?

00:39:42.910 --> 00:39:45.190
What does that mean?

00:39:45.190 --> 00:39:47.530
That's one of those
really interesting things.

00:39:47.530 --> 00:39:49.600
And I know the tech
