00:42:28.770 --> 00:42:30.120
LATHA PALANIAPPAN: Absolutely.

00:42:30.120 --> 00:42:31.960
I completely agree with you.

00:42:31.960 --> 00:42:34.050
And to restate a
little bit is sort

00:42:34.050 --> 00:42:37.200
of like there were some broad
strokes about diabetes rates

00:42:37.200 --> 00:42:41.760
and sort of an ecological
sort of argument

00:42:41.760 --> 00:42:44.490
that increased diabetes
is caused by increased

00:42:44.490 --> 00:42:47.460
