a 24-hour food recall.

00:43:14.935 --> 00:43:16.560
So that's what we do
with our patients,

00:43:16.560 --> 00:43:18.930
like seeing what they
ate in the last 24 hours.

00:43:18.930 --> 00:43:21.480
