can be more protein

00:43:21.480 --> 00:43:24.600
and a substitution for more of
a whole grain than a refined

00:43:24.600 --> 00:43:25.230
grain.

00:43:25.230 --> 00:43:27.810
And some of these interventions
that are culturally specific,

00:43:27.810 --> 00:43:29.550
