aerobic training only,

00:44:08.300 --> 00:44:09.760
or a combination of both.

00:44:09.760 --> 00:44:11.550
So I agree, there's
plenty of room

00:44:11.550 --> 00:44:15.090
for fine tuning both diet
and exercise that should

00:44:15.090 --> 00:44:18.610
be done on an individual level.

00:44:18.610 --> 00:44:19.444
So I agree with you.

00:44:19.444 --> 00:44:21.609
